{"tid":9951,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人會拎ip7去沖涼？","createTime":"2016-11-28T18:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T05:51:26.000Z","uid":7049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1205250919ad32688ad08b77cd1e33e7af80f3","tid":9951,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"Iphone7講話防水 但又話會因用耐左而慢慢冇防水<br />\n咁到底用到幾時先冇防水功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇人真係會拎去沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見有時整污糟左都拎去洗洗<br />\n好似好方便咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0c564d4a54d65447501d287ac33dd5e8f22ec4","tid":9951,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:24:16.000Z","msg":"3GS果陣都有拎啦  不過冇整濕咋嘛<img src=\"http://goo.gl/vUaArF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FvUaArF&h=77fca880&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"77c46cee92ea0cc6fc2d95e825c3722c7ca0acbf","tid":9951,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:25:13.000Z","msg":"我間唔中都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a8b71ef36b42fb8ccec48750cb3ff7cafcd68f","tid":9951,"uid":16014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:26:28.000Z","msg":"依家有電話入會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9252f2dd2ad9b2c815a061e15121e864ee719014","tid":9951,"uid":12265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:27:20.000Z","msg":"我5已經會，邊沖涼邊聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2a9ae93c8d8c5853c79d512d5bdbc4efbecda5","tid":9951,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"成部iPad mini 拎入去廁所，一路沖天路煲劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6ec3ffb23e0f57358f451d9b9e9f61ef5cc443","tid":9951,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成部iPad mini 拎入去廁所，一路沖天路煲劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niPad 我會入密實袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922bdfa660c9a0a6e1552335533c035d62af2fc2","tid":9951,"uid":2275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:35:55.000Z","msg":"iPhone 5S 到而家 iPhone 7 都係拎入去聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f077b67d59b3281c768adb8d3c08770d66b489","tid":9951,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:46:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成部iPad mini 拎入去廁所，一路沖天路煲劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\niPad 我會入密實袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會，但放係一個花洒冇咁易走火彈中嘅位<br />\n咁多年黎都慣左拎電話/pda/pad 一路沖一路聽歌上網煲劇，試過幾次跌左部機落地浸幾秒水，乾番又冇事，亦都未試過受潮壞機<br />\n最灰嗰次係跌左部z5p, 爆左個鏡面底，番廠整左200蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"636d49e6fca0d583eb8277ee862a48d361293868","tid":9951,"uid":18573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:11:04.000Z","msg":"會攞iPad mini入廁所聽歌睇戲唔怕濕<br />\n但電話iPhone6試過一次跑步跑到啲汗入水之後唔敢再攞電語入廁所只用iPad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846ca484a674bc6b09fb855237955d3e33d96def","tid":9951,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:16:49.000Z","msg":"你有冇聽過水冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eae08e836f479ae10dcd4791fe2dc734916593","tid":9951,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T19:21:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你有冇聽過水冷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/IGAW6I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FIGAW6I&h=57c8a710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"499891b827aec35e34a412a59fc256f395a280f0","tid":9951,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T20:01:42.000Z","msg":"擺埋一邊播歌"},{"pid":"b30abb3419910e8729b5999ea5fab82a60f69561","tid":9951,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:12:59.000Z","msg":"防水同防蒸氣好似兩樣野來？"},{"pid":"c07669f413fe50c5cbdf11980bfa5f121adab79b","tid":9951,"uid":26592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"一邊沖一邊用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5632e20f70c0350f2754ed4fa8a9f9b28ddf844","tid":9951,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T03:49:30.000Z","msg":"試過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 花灑射同成部浸落水都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23357c511c84c0d9d04717fd0577cbcbb4e1832c","tid":9951,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"一邊叉電一邊睇"},{"pid":"d8300732ebfdf16feaeff2de394ff0edd32d03d0","tid":9951,"uid":839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T04:32:18.000Z","msg":"有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131aa2fcfd233f306fd0938ba83b025bd3402aa7","tid":9951,"uid":15491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":