ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之祝你地好運啦，係我就唔會打入去沖涼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8a500b3b4e4acfedc05cd8ab3f1f8b53cf8b38","tid":9951,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"It's water-resistant, not waterproof. Apple stated that liquid damage is not covered under warranty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}